Wild Heart Collection Is Online Now.
'Your Passion + Your Action = A Beautiful World for Animals.'

This collection aims to create captivating images through the lens of fashion, encouraging people to learn about and care for animals across all species.

node.text:
🌏 SHEIN Cares For Animals 🌏

SHEIN is on a mission to protect the animals! Since we share the same home, we should consider animals our friends and do what we can to keep them safe. Let's join together to keep our animals protected!

The more we understand, the more ways we can have to help. That's why we created a fun game to help you learn more about the world's most adorable creatures.

For your chance to WIN 💚:⁣⁣⁣
🐬 Follow @sheinofficial & like this post.
🐧 Comment on your favorite animal emoji. (🐘, 🦘, 🦓, 🦒....)
🦏 Share the pic during the interactive game in the APP '#SHEINcares For Animals' as an IG post with the hashtag #SHEINcares

🔗 https://shein.top/e0vkp0l

Prizes:⁠
𝙂𝙧𝙖𝙣𝙙 𝙋𝙧𝙞𝙯𝙚: $𝟱𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨 * 𝟳
𝙎𝙚𝙘𝙤𝙣𝙙 𝙋𝙧𝙞𝙯𝙚: $𝟯𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨 & 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙒𝙞𝙡𝙙 𝙃𝙚𝙖𝙧𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙡𝙡𝙚𝙘𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙥𝙧𝙤𝙙𝙪𝙘𝙩𝙨 *𝟭𝟬
𝙏𝙝𝙞𝙧𝙙 𝙋𝙧𝙞𝙯𝙚: $𝟭𝟬𝟬 𝙎𝙃𝙀𝙄𝙉 𝙂𝙞𝙛𝙩 𝘾𝙤𝙙𝙚𝙨 * 𝟮𝟬

Winners will be announced on 8/30 in our story! Stay tuned for our upcoming #SHEINcares events.

👉 Please Note:⁣⁠
1. Your accounts need to be public so that we can see your entries.⁣⁠
2. The gift code needs to have an email address registered to a SHEIN account. Multiple winners with the same address would be treated as one winner with one gift code.⁠
